question: Table tsiah ū kúi-ê chènn-phìnn thè-chhut ê kók-chū pí "bē-tàng su-miā" koh-khah-hó?
Hui director ū siâu-chúi ê kòe-thong, tùi tit tio̍h siōng koân ê chióng kàu bô tit tio̍h miâ ê chha̍p hāng, ū siángngá?
answer: Pedro Almodóvar sī chin ū chin chē chióng kòe-thong ê director. I ê tiān-iáⁿ 'All About My Mother' tit tio̍h Academy Award, 'Volver [4 ]' tòe-tio̍h January Shortlist, koh 'High Heels' bô tit tio̍h miâ, chiap-siūⁿ chū choân-pō͘ ê tui-chiap chi̍t ê kòe-thong tùi téng-kip ê sêng-kong kàu chho͘-kî thè-chhut.

question: Na ke hō͘ chò 'Nominee' ê chhiám-phian ê miâ-chheng, sī siâng chi̍t ê lâng chòe-chú-tō ê 'Cradle Song' lâi chòe ê?
Tī chit ê phiau. chhap lāi, chhap 1990 nî-tāi (1991-1999 nî ê ián-chhut nî-tāi) ê chè-tāi chhut-phín, iâng-ūi chòe--sī chòe ê chìn-chiok ê chōan-koân, ē-tàng kám-siàu án-chóaⁿ？
answer: 1990 nî-tāi ê chhut-phín phiau. chhap sī chiap-kīn kiông-sîm ê chìn-chiok. chit ê cha̍p-nî khai-sí, 1991 kap 1992 nî ê chham-chiàⁿ chè-tāi bô hō͘ jīm-bēng. put-kò, āu-lâi chiap-chhut chin tōa ê tit-chú, pau-koat 1993 nî ('Belle Époque') kap 1999 nî ('All About My Mother') ê chè-tāi tit-chú nn̄g ki Oscar kim-chiòng, kap chi̍t ki 1998 nî ('The Grandfather') ê chè-tāi jīm-bēng. chit ē tō ián-sī chhut chham-chiàⁿ chè-tāi ê kok-chè jīn-tiāⁿ sī lâi-kàu khoài-sok ê chi̍t ê sî-kî.

question: 2000年代 陣 '落選' 條件  ê 電影 提名片名 紀錄。
Tī chitê lia̍t-toa̍u, tùi 2000 nî kàu 2009 nî ê Tiān-iáⁿ-chè (ceremony years) tiong, ū kúi-pho phah jīm the̍h-chè Oscar chiong?
Tng-ji̍t 'Tristana' chiap-siū Academy Award tō-sī kan-tann sī tsi̍t uī tsı̂-tāi，luē-pīnn Lú Sū Buñuel teh tsiañ ê siú-chiàn tiān-iáⁿ ê sin tsóng-sè sī to-tsōa?
answer: Sin ê tsóng-sè ē-sī 1. Taⁿ, Lú Sū Buñuel teh tsiañ ê tiān-iáⁿ bô ti̍t-tet siú-chiàn, só͘-í kā 'Tristana' ê tsı̂-tāi tsuán-uānn tsiânn 'siú-chiàn' ē-sī kā i ê tsóng-sè tsiânn 0 kàu 1.

question: Bē-tùi tsu-liāu lâi koan-tshàm, tshiúñ-ba̍k ê miâ hām in ê guân-tiāu tshiúñ sī kāng-ê, in tit-tio̍h Oscar ê ki-huē ū tsi̍t-tsóng tsiânn-lâi ê koan-hē bô?
answer: Bô gōan-lâi ê koan-hē. Teh jīm-hô tit-tio̍h Oscar ê sann-ê tshiúñ lāi-bīn, nn̄g-ê ū kāng-ê miâ ('All About My Mother' hām 'The Sea Inside'), tān-sī tsi̍t-ê koh bô kāng-ê miâ ('Belle Époque'). In-siann sī kóng, tshiúñ-ba̍k ê miâ bô kāng hām tit-tio̍h Oscar bô tsiánn-tshiánn ê koan-hē.

question: Koh chiat-chham ūi-tiāⁿ ū chi̍t ê siông-koân, hui-siông-e̍k ê bûn-jī-choāⁿ hō͘ thun-siâⁿ kàu múi chi̍t ê luī-pia̍h?
Tī só͘-chāi chu-liāu lāi, siáⁿ chi̍t ê cha̍p-nî-tāi ê Akademy Chióng the̍h tit ê siâⁿ-chiok-chū sò͘-liōng, tùi pa̍t-chi̍t-ê cha̍p-nî-tāi lâi kóng, sī chi̍t ê ''outlier''?
answer: 1990 nî-tāi sī chi̍t ê ''outlier'', ū nn̄g chiah chèⁿ-phìⁿ ('All About My Mother' kap 'Belle Époque') the̍h tio̍h Akademy Chióng. Tùi tùi-chhiat lâi kóng, 2000 nî-tāi kan-na chi̍t chiah iâⁿ-chiáⁿ, koh ū pa̍t-chi̍t-ê khó-tiâu ê cha̍p-nî-tāi (1950 nî-tāi, 1960 nî-tāi, 1970 nî-tāi, 1980 nî-tāi, 2010 nî-tāi) lóng bô iâⁿ-chiáⁿ, chiâⁿ chòe 1990 nî-tāi ê sêng-kong luī sī chiok koân ê chi̍t ê pó͘-tē.

question: Chiah-sī Pedro Almodóvar tī 1995-nî ê tiān-iáⁿ ài siū-miâ, i ê chóng siū-miâ-ê sò͘ ē cháiⁿ-iūⁿ kái-piàn?
answer: I ē tit-iâⁿ i ê chóng siū-miâ tùi 4-ê kàu 5-ê.
